      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Git流程图，展示如何把feature分支合并到main分支。标题就叫\"Merge feature to advanced main\"，方向用从上到下的布局。",
      "elements_involved": [
