    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，TB就是从上到下的方向。分支名就用\"newbranch\"吧，保持简洁。流程是：先在main上初始化提交，然后切出来newbranch做开发，最后再checkout回main进行merge。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "newbranch",
        "checkout",
        "commit",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画个初稿。main分支上有一个初始commit，然后分出newbranch，newbranch上有一个commit，之后切回main再提交一次，最后把newbranch合并进来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "branch newbranch",
        "checkout newbranch",
        "checkout main",
        "merge newbranch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，标题我漏了一个字母，应该是\"advanced\"不是\"advaced\"。还有方向标注要完整，是\"top-to-bottom\"不是\"top to bottom\"，需要加上连字符。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "advanced",
        "top-to-bottom"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，标题修正为\"Merge feature to advanced main (top-to-bottom)\"，连字符也补上了。我检查一下分支流向：newbranch的commit在merge时能正确连接到main的最新commit吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "merge newbranch",
        "main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，这样merge节点会同时连接main的第二个commit和newbranch的commit，形成正确的合并图。整个流程清晰展示了分支开发再合并的典型场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge",
